---
// SocialProof.astro — Editorial pull-quote social proof
---

<section id="social-proof" class="social-proof-section">
  <div class="social-proof-inner">
    <h2 class="sr-only">What teams are saying</h2>

    <!-- Credibility line -->
    <div class="credibility-row" data-reveal>
      <div class="accent-dash" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="credibility-content">
        <div class="trusted-line">
          <span class="trusted-label">Trusted by teams at</span>
          <strong>JetBrains</strong>
          <span class="trusted-sep">/</span>
          <strong>Adeo</strong>
          <span class="trusted-sep">/</span>
          <strong>Bundeswehr</strong>
        </div>
        <p class="credibility-tagline">5+ years of ML orchestration, now applied to agents.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Quotes row -->
    <div class="quotes-row" data-reveal>
      <blockquote class="primary-quote">
        <span class="quote-mark" aria-hidden="true">&ldquo;</span>
        <p>We were spending 40% of our agent development time on retry logic and state recovery. Kitaru replaced all of that with two decorators.</p>
        <footer>— <cite>ML Platform Lead, Series B AI Company</cite></footer>
      </blockquote>
      <blockquote class="secondary-quote">
        <p>The replay capability alone saved us thousands in LLM costs during development. Being able to resume from a checkpoint instead of re-running everything is a game-changer.</p>
        <footer>— <cite>Staff Engineer, Enterprise MLOps Team</cite></footer>
      </blockquote>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .social-proof-section {
    background: var(--color-accent-light);
    padding: 120px 0;
  }

  .social-proof-inner {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 clamp(24px, 5vw, 80px);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 80px;
  }

  /* ── Credibility line ── */
  .credibility-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .accent-dash {
    width: 40px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  .credibility-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .trusted-line {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .trusted-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    line-height: 14px;
  }

  .trusted-line strong {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    line-height: 18px;
  }

  .trusted-sep {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    line-height: 18px;
  }

  .credibility-tagline {
    font-size: clamp(24px, 3vw, 36px);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ── Quotes row ── */
  .quotes-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 60px;
  }

  .primary-quote {
    flex: 3 1 0%;
    position: relative;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .primary-quote p {
    font-size: 28px;
    line-height: 40px;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 48px;
  }

  .quote-mark {
    position: absolute;
    top: -20px;
    left: -16px;
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 160px;
    line-height: 100px;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    opacity: 0.15;
    pointer-events: none;
    user-select: none;
  }

  .secondary-quote {
    flex: 2 1 0%;
    border-left: 1px solid oklch(0.15 0.02 60 / 0.1);
    padding-left: 40px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    flex-direction: column;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .secondary-quote p {
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 28px;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    font-style: italic;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .primary-quote footer,
  .secondary-quote footer {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    margin-top: 16px;
    padding-left: 48px;
  }

  .secondary-quote footer {
    padding-left: 0;
  }

  .primary-quote cite,
  .secondary-quote cite {
    font-style: normal;
  }

  /* ── Mobile ── */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .social-proof-section {
      padding: 80px 0;
    }

    .social-proof-inner {
      gap: 48px;
    }

    .credibility-tagline {
      font-size: 20px;
      line-height: 26px;
    }

    .quotes-row {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 40px;
    }

    .primary-quote p {
      font-size: 22px;
      line-height: 32px;
      padding-left: 40px;
    }

    .quote-mark {
      font-size: 100px;
      line-height: 70px;
      top: -14px;
      left: -10px;
    }

    .secondary-quote {
      border-left: none;
      border-top: 1px solid oklch(0.15 0.02 60 / 0.1);
      padding-left: 0;
      padding-top: 32px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .social-proof-section { padding: 60px 0; }
    .social-proof-inner { gap: 32px; }
    .credibility-tagline { font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; }
    .primary-quote p { font-size: 18px; line-height: 28px; padding-left: 32px; }
    .quote-mark { font-size: 80px; line-height: 60px; }
    .secondary-quote p { font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; }
    .primary-quote footer { padding-left: 32px; }
  }
</style>
